<li><a href="#unsafe-or-unlicensed-contractors">Unsafe or unlicensed contractors</a></li>
<li><a href="#complaints-or-general-information">Complaints or general information</a></li>
<li><a href="#media-inquiries">Media inquiries</a></li>
</ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <!-- End WYSIWYG content -->
    
    
  
  <div class="one-quarter-layout">
          <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="district-offices">District offices</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <div class="callout "> You can visit the L&amp;I district offices to get help with requesting a statement of outstanding fees for re-inspections and case-files, requesting a status of your violation and permit, and getting general information about complying a violation on your property or about general eCLIPSE related questions. The district offices can&#8217;t process applications or payments at this time.</p>
<p>You must schedule your inspections <a href="https://eclipse.phila.gov/phillylmsprod/pub/lms/Login.aspx">online using eCLIPSE</a> or through the <a href="https://www.phila.gov/documents/inspection-scheduling-materials/">IVR system</a> by calling <a href="tel:2152554040">(215) 255-4040</a>.</div>
<p>L&amp;I inspectors are stationed at district offices across Philadelphia.</p>
<div class="row mbl">
<div class="medium-8 columns vr"><strong>East District</strong><br />
7522 Castor Ave.<br />
Philadelphia, PA 19152<br />
Code Enforcement Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156850535">(215) 685-0535</a><br />
<a href="mailto:codeenforcement.east@phila.gov">Email</a><br />
Construction Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156850580">(215) 685-0580</a> or <a href="tel:2156850583">(215) 685-0583</a><br />
<a href="mailto:construction.east@phila.gov">Email</a></div>
<div class="medium-8 columns vr"><strong>North District</strong><br />
1512-14 Cecil B. Moore Ave.<br />
Philadelphia, PA 19121<br />
Code Enforcement Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156830575">(215) 683-0575</a><br />
<a href="mailto:codeenforcement.north@phila.gov">Email</a><br />
Construction Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156830580">(215) 683-0580</a> or <a href="tel:2156830584">(215) 683-0584</a><br />
<a href="mailto:construction.north@phila.gov">Email</a></div>
<div class="medium-8 columns vr"><strong>Central West District</strong><br />
2401 Walnut St., Suite 502<br />
Philadelphia, PA 19103<br />
Code Enforcement Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156862596">(215) 686-2596</a><br />
<a href="mailto:codeenforcement.centralwest@phila.gov">Email</a><br />
Construction Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156853789">(215) 685-3789</a> or <a href="tel:2156853790">(215) 685-3790</a><br />
<a href="mailto:construction.centralwest@phila.gov">Email</a></div>
</div>
<div class="row mbl">
<div class="medium-8 columns vr"><strong>South District</strong><br />
1100 Wharton St., 2nd Floor<br />
Philadelphia, PA 19147<br />
Code Enforcement Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156851510">(215) 685-1510</a><br />
<a href="mailto:codeenforcement.south@phila.gov">Email</a><br />
Construction Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156851576">(215) 685-1576</a> or <a href="tel:2156851578">(215) 685-1578</a><br />
<a href="mailto:construction.south@phila.gov">Email</a></div>
<div class="medium-8 columns vr"><strong>Central East District</strong><br />
667 N. Broad St., 3rd floor<br />
Philadelphia, PA 19123<br />
Code Enforcement Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156853917">(215) 685-3917</a><br />
<a href="mailto:codeenforcement.centraleast@phila.gov">Email</a><br />
Construction Unit<br />
<a href="tel:2156853786">(215) 685-3786</a>, <a href="tel:2156853787">3787</a>, <a href="tel:2156853788">3788</a><br />
<a href="mailto:construction.centraleast@phila.gov">Email</a></div>
</div>
<p>You can also use the map to find districts and district offices.</p>
<style>.embed-container {position: relative; padding-bottom: 100%; height: 0; max-width: 100%;} .embed-container iframe, .embed-container object, .embed-container iframe{position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;} small{position: absolute; z-index: 40; bottom: 0; margin-bottom: -15px;}</style>
<div class="embed-container"><iframe title="L&amp;I Districts and District Offices" src="//phl.maps.arcgis.com/apps/Embed/index.html?webmap=c13b0909c46a4367a61017baf30b6ca2&amp;extent=-75.4012,39.8777,-74.8368,40.1322&amp;zoom=true&amp;previewImage=false&amp;scale=true&amp;search=true&amp;searchextent=false&amp;disable_scroll=true&amp;theme=light&amp;logoimage=false" width="500" height="500" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></div>
<h3 class="mtm">Districts and district offices</h3>
<ul class="map-legend">
<li class="map-orange map-color">Districts</li>
<li class="map-purple map-color">District offices</li>
</ul>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="notice-of-completed-repairs">Notice of completed repairs</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For notice of completed repairs, submit the <a class="external" href="https://form.jotform.com/200817695228057">notice of completed repairs form</a> to the Department of Licenses and Inspections (L&amp;I) or call <a href="tel:311">311</a> or <a href="tel:2156868686">(215) 686-8686</a> if outside Philadelphia.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="license-questions">License questions</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For help navigating eCLIPSE with submitting your license application, you can engage in a <a href="https://eclipse.phila.gov/phillylmsprod/pub/lms/Login.aspx">Chat</a> session. The Chat hours are between 9:00 a.m. to 1:00 p.m.</p>
<p>To speak with a License Issuance agent, you must schedule a <a href="https://www.phila.gov/services/permits-violations-licenses/make-an-appointment-with-the-permit-and-license-center/">virtual or in-person appointment</a>.</p>
<p>For all other licensing questions, <a href="https://form.jotform.com/202434637485055">submit an online request</a> to the Department of Licenses and Inspections (L&amp;I) . You will receive a response within 2 business days.</p>
<p>For general questions, call <a href="tel:311">311</a> or <a href="tel:2156868686">(215) 686-8686</a> if outside Philadelphia.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="permit-and-code-questions">Permit and code questions</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <table class="dcf-table dcf-table-responsive dcf-table-bordered dcf-table-striped dcf-w-100%">
<thead>
<tr>
<th scope="col">Resources</th>
<th scope="col">Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-label="Resources"><a href="https://www.phila.gov/services/permits-violations-licenses/make-an-appointment-with-the-permit-and-license-center/">In-Person appointment</a></td>
<td data-label="Description">Submit paper applications.</p>
<p>Plan pick-up.</p>
<p>Copy requests.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-label="Resources"><a href="https://www.phila.gov/services/permits-violations-licenses/make-an-appointment-with-the-permit-and-license-center/">Virtual appointment</a></td>
<td data-label="Description">Assistance with filing new electronic applications, including make-safe permits and permit fee waivers.</p>
<p>Questions about electronic application rejection (prior to examiner review).</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-label="Resources"><a href="https://eclipse.phila.gov/phillylmsprod/pub/lms/Login.aspx">Chat session</a></p>
<p>(9:00 a.m. &#8211; 1:00 p.m.)</td>
<td data-label="Description">For help navigating eCLIPSE.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-label="Resources">Plans examination appointment</td>
<td data-label="Description">Request a <a href="https://www.phila.gov/services/permits-violations-licenses/get-construction-approval-and-review/get-approval-for-construction-in-the-floodplain/">flood protection scoping meeting</a>.</p>
<p>Request a <a href="https://www.phila.gov/services/permits-violations-licenses/get-construction-approval-and-review/get-a-project-scoping-meeting-for-a-multi-phased-project/">multi-phased project scoping meeting</a>.</p>
<p><a href="https://form.jotform.com/83434300042139">Schedule an appointment with an L&amp;I examiner</a> to discuss additional information requested on an open application.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-label="Resources"><a href="https://www.phila.gov/services/permits-violations-licenses/get-construction-approval-and-review/request-a-preliminary-review-of-construction-projects/">Preliminary review</a></td>
<td data-label="Description">Request a preliminary project meeting or a preliminary plan review.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-label="Resources"><a href="https://form.jotform.com/202434637485055">Online help form</a></td>
<td data-label="Description">Code and processing questions.</p>
<p>Request a release on a permit issuance hold.</p>
<p>Status of a late review.</p>
<p>Other permit related questions.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-label="Resources"><a href="tel:311">311</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:2156868686">(215) 686-8686</a> if outside Philadelphia</td>
<td data-label="Description">For general questions.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="property-certifications">Property <br>certifications </h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For property certification questions, <a class="external" href="https://form.jotform.com/202434637485055">submit an online request</a> to the Department of Licenses and Inspections (L&amp;I).</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="appeals">Appeals</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For questions about <a href="https://www.phila.gov/departments/board-of-building-standards/">Board of Building Standards</a> (BBS), <a href="https://www.phila.gov/departments/plumbing-advisory-board/">Plumbing Advisory Board</a> (PAB), and <a href="https://www.phila.gov/departments/board-of-license-and-inspection-review/">Board of Licenses and Inspections Review</a> (BLIR) appeals, call <a href="tel:2156862419">(215) 686-2419</a> or email <a href="mailto:BoardsAdmin@phila.gov">BoardsAdmin@phila.gov</a>.</p>
<p>You can also mail comments to:</p>
<p>Boards Administration<br />
1401 John F. Kennedy Blvd., 11th Floor<br />
Philadelphia, PA 19102</p>
<p>To file an appeal with the BLIR, BBS, or PAB, you must schedule an <a href="https://www.phila.gov/services/permits-violations-licenses/make-an-appointment-with-the-permit-and-license-center/">in-person appointment</a>.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="dangerous-buildings">Dangerous buildings</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>In the case of an emergency, call <a href="tel:911">911</a>.</p>
<p>For other inquiries about dangerous buildings, call <a href="tel:2156862480">(215) 686-2480</a> or email <a href="mailto:Stephen.gallagher@phila.gov">Stephen.Gallagher@phila.gov</a>.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="vending">Vending</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For questions about vending, call <a href="tel:2156862414">(215) 686-2414</a> or email <a href="mailto:vending@phila.gov">Vending@phila.gov</a>.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="vacant-properties">Vacant properties</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For vacant property questions, email <a href="mailto:VacantPropertyUnit@phila.gov">VacantPropertyUnit@phila.gov</a></p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="nuisance-properties">Nuisance properties</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For nuisance property questions, call <a href="tel:2156862515">(215) 686-2515</a> or email <a href="mailto:NuisancePropertyUnit@phila.gov">NuisancePropertyUnit@phila.gov</a>.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="property-abatement-bills">Property abatement bills</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>If a property violation is abated using City funds, the property owner is billed for this work.</p>
<p>For a copy of the original invoice that includes details about work done at a property, email <a href="mailto:LIebills@phila.gov">LIebills@phila.gov</a>. Original invoices will not list any accrued interest or penalty charges.</p>
<p>To view or pay the invoice, including any interest and penalty charges, visit the <a href="https://tax-services.phila.gov/">Philadelphia Tax Center</a>. Navigate to the &#8220;Property&#8221; section, then select &#8220;Search for a property&#8221; to find invoices, liens and debts, and to make a payment.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="audits-and-investigations">Audits and investigations</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For audit and investigation questions, call <a href="tel:2156862499">(215) 686-2499</a> or email <a href="mailto:AIU@phila.gov">AIU@phila.gov</a>.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="litigation">Litigation</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <h4>Questions</h4>
<p>For questions about subpoenas, the Tax Review Board, right-to-know requests, and Municipal Court or Equity Court, call <a href="tel:2156861441">(215) 686-1441</a>/<a href="tel:2156861442">1442</a>.</p>
<hr />
<h4>File a right-to-know request</h4>
<p>Refer to the <a class="" href="https://www.phila.gov/open-records-policy/">City’s Open Records Policy</a> for instructions on how to file a right-to-know request.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="unsafe-or-unlicensed-contractors">Unsafe or unlicensed <br>contractors</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>To report unlicensed contractors or unpermitted work, use <a href="https://iframe.publicstuff.com/#?client_id=242">311’s online form</a> or call <a href="tel:311">311</a>. If you&#8217;re outside Philadelphia, call <a href="tel:2156868686">(215) 686-8686</a>.</p>
<p>After you’ve filed a report with 311, you can submit more information to <a href="mailto:addinfoli@phila.gov">addinfoli@phila.gov</a>. Include the 311 case number, address where work is being done, and your phone number or email address.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="complaints-or-general-information">Complaints or <br>general information</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For complaints or general information, use <a href="https://iframe.publicstuff.com/#?client_id=242">311&#8217;s online form</a> or call <a href="tel:311">311</a>. If you&#8217;re outside Philadelphia, call <a href="tel:2156868686">(215) 686-8686</a>.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
                  <hr class="margin-auto"/>
                  <div class="row one-quarter-row mvxl">
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
            <h3 id="media-inquiries">Media inquiries</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="medium-18 columns pbxl">
                                                            <p>For media inquiries, contact the Mayor&#8217;s Communications Office at <a href="mailto:press@phila.gov">Press@phila.gov</a>.</p>
            
            
                                  </div>
        </div>
              </div>
